text: "Jump Right In" is a 2013 song by country band Zac Brown Band and is the third single from their third studio album Uncaged. It went to number 53 in the United States, number 63 in Canada and went to number 3 on the Canadian Billboard country charts and number 13 on the Billboard Hot Country Song charts. It was written by Jason Mraz. ==References== Category:2013 songs Category:Country songs Category:Zac Brown Band songs
title: Jump Right In
